Package com.sinch.xms.api

Class MtBatchSmsResult

java.lang.Object
com.sinch.xms.api.MtBatchSmsResult
Direct Known Subclasses:
MtBatchBinarySmsResult, MtBatchTextSmsResult
public abstract class MtBatchSmsResult
extends Object
Base class for batch description classes. This contains the fields common for both textual and binary batches.
